event.text:
Alright team. Here's the plan:

@server — you own shared types (#1), server components (#2), and CLI (#3). Start with types — they're the critical path. Both client and fixtures are blocked until types land.

@client — you own scaffolding (#4) and full implementation (#5). Blocked on #1. Use the wait to read the spec docs.

@fixtures — you own fixture generator (#6), package config (#7), and integration tests (#8). #6 and #7 can start immediately. #8 is blocked on #2 and #6.

Everyone: require plan approval before you start coding. I want to see your implementation plans first.
